title: Ready to take the leap? 1
thought-description: If you feel like something isn’t quite right but the road you are on is at least predictable and safe, it’s not an easy task to find the courage to choose the lesser known path. There are a lot of what-ifs standing in your way. Fear of the unknown is a big obstacle.
